Usage: open_schematic [-help] [-name <string>] [-type {module cone}] [-objects <inst|net|instTerm|term|hInst>+ | -selected ]

-help                                    # Prints out the command usage
-name <string>                           # Specify unique window name for the
                                         # opening schematic view.
                                         # (string, optional)
-objects <inst|net|instTerm|term|hInst>+
                                         # Specify the objects which are added
                                         # in the schematic view.
                                         # ((inst|net|instTerm|term|hInst)+, optional)
-selected                                # Specify selected objects which are
                                         # added in the schematic view.
                                         # (bool, optional)
-type {module cone}                      # Specify the opened type of
                                         # schematic. (enum, optional)